These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
2 different pets are kept: dog, ferret
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, engineer
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, old-henry
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, poppy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, october
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Pet         | ferret  | dog       |
| Job           | engineer   | accountant    |
| Cigar   | old-henry     | game   |
| Flower   | poppy      | amaryllis     |
| Sport         | volleyball | swimming      |
| Birthday     | october       | june           |

