.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, havana
There 2 different types of food: avocado, strawberry
House: ranch-style, wooden
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, may
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, turkish
There are 2 different favourite colors: ebony, purple
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, van
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Cigar      | havana         | oliveros       |
| Food          | avocado        | strawberry |
| House           | wooden | ranch-style    |
| Birthday   | may        | march  |
| Nationality   | turkish        | thai       |
| Color           | purple            | ebony        |
| Transport     | van            | ship       |

