2. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | water       | coffee     |
