2. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
5. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching action movies##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Nationality      | indonesian    | italian   |
| City         | edinburgh | nizza |
